dex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jgx1665702723636.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jgx1665702723636.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jgx1665702723636.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jgx1665702723636\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specifies how to render the TextArea control for a non-editable field (NED) in static server pages.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"jgx1665702723636__topic_d143636e1_d143637e1_d143638e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jgx1665702723636__p_d143639e1_d143640e1_d143641e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$USP_NED_TEXTAREA</span> { <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code> } <code class=\"ph codeph\">readonly</code> |\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">plaintext</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jgx1665702723636__section_hlg_1vm_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d709734e67\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"jgx1665702723636__ul_okh_bvm_lwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jgx1665702723636__li_d50234e1_d50235e1_d50236e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">readonly</code>—renders the contol as a\n               TextArea widget with the attribute NED (non-editable). This is the default. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"jgx1665702723636__li_d50237e1_d50238e1_d50239e1\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">plaintext</code>—renders the control as\n               plain text. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jgx1665702723636__section_f53_cvm_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d709734e86\">Defaults</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jgx1665702723636__table_d17348e1_d17349e1_d17350e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Any application assignment file</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">[SETTINGS]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">readonly</code></td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jgx1665702723636__section_kl5_fvm_lwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d709734e133\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jgx1665702723636__p_d143651e1_d143652e1_d143653e1\">Prior to Uniface 9, a non-editable field (field\n            syntax <code class=\"ph codeph\">NED</code>) with the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">HTML Control</span> type set to\n               <code class=\"ph codeph\">TextArea</code>, was rendered as plain text in the HTML layout. Since\n            Uniface 9, it is rendered as a TextArea widget with the <code class=\"ph codeph\">readonly</code>\n            attribute.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jgx1665702723636__p_d143654e1_d143655e1_d143656e1\">Use this assignment setting only if you need the\n            old behavior.</p>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ilc1719468669617.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>TextArea</a><p>The TextArea widget represents a text field in a static server page and can be used to display and enter data on multiple lines.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528870\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2528870\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$USP_NED_TEXTAREA Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specifies how to render the TextArea control for a non-editable field (NED) in static server pages. $USP_NED_TEXTAREA { = } readonly | plaintext Arguments readonly —renders the contol as a TextArea widget with the attribute NED (non-editable). This is the default. plaintext —renders the control as plain text. Defaults Assignment file: Any application assignment file Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: readonly Description Prior to Uniface 9, a non-editable field (field syntax NED ) with the HTML Control type set to TextArea , was rendered as plain text in the HTML layout. Since Uniface 9, it is rendered as a TextArea widget with the readonly attribute. Use this assignment setting only if you need the old behavior. Related Links TextArea The TextArea widget represents a text field in a static server page and can be used to display and enter data on multiple lines. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}